What to get for the whiskey lovers or what to bring to a holiday party? How about a bottle of @rabbithole Boxergrail.
Crafted with the eye of a prizefighter, Boxergrail is a robust Kentucky Straight Rye Whiskey that dances across the palate. inspired by the season’s produce 
• Satsuma with bourbon, tangerine juice, lemon, orange-saffron syrup & dried orange

Welcome to the @holbrookehotel where modern luxuries blend seamlessly with a historically unique, rustic-yet-refined, one-of-a-kind property.
